  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You succeed at your save against a foe's harmful spell, or a foe fails a spell attack roll against you from a harmful spell.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>When you resist a spell, you capture some of its magic for your own use. You enter your Arcane Cascade stance, using the triggering spell to determine what damage type your Arcane Cascade deals.</p>\n<p>Alternatively, if you're already in Arcane Cascade, you can instead amplify its effects temporarily. Until the end of your next turn, you gain a +2 status bonus to the damage from your Arcane Cascade.</p>"
